mknod -m 600 /dev/console c 5 1 || true
mknod -m 666 /dev/null c 1 3 || true

printf "\

Welcome to AOSC OS (with the brand new Core 3.4.0)!

Core 3.4.0 is a feature update for AOSC OS Core.

	- Linux API headers (linux+api) is updated to 4.4.1;
	- Binutils (binutils) is updated to 2.26.0;
        - International Timezone Data (tzdata) is updated to 2016a;
        - GNU Multiple Precision Library (gmp) is updated to 6.1.0;

For any issue encountered in the future, please report them as an Issue at

https://github.com/AOSC-Dev/aosc-os-core/issues/

"
